# Selectors & Data

## Selectors

- Prefer `data-testid` when the app exposes stable test IDs
- When testing Conduit (an app we don't control), use role/accessible-name locators (`getByRole`)
- Avoid CSS unless stable; never use XPath
- Selectors live in page objects — not in spec files

## Test Data

- Test data via fixtures + factories; no hardcoded data

## Secrets & Config

- No hardcoded secrets, base URLs, or tokens — read from env/config only
